All functions

antlers

Simulated data on the effects of diet on deer antlers.

AOU_species_codes

American Ornithological Union (AOU) species codes for North-American birds

BBS_PA

Pennsylvania Breeding Survey Data (BBS) from the USGS.

BBS_PA_combo_cover_1km

Combinations of NLCD land cover classes into more general groups for Pennsylvania, USA.

BBS_PA_landcover_1km

Land cover buffers from the 1 km surrounding Breeding Bird Survey Routes (BBS) in Pennsylvania

BBS_PA_SCTA

Number of Scarlet tanagers (SCTA) observed on Pennsylvania BBS routes in 2006 and total forested landcover in 1km buffers around routes

brook_trout

Brook trout impacts on Chinook salmon survival - original data

brook_trout_ABD

Impact of brook trout on survival of Chinook salmon in Idaho.

combine_NLCD_classes

Combine multiple landcover classes into a single combined group

doves_PA

PA Mourning doves

eggs

Bird eggs datatset.

eggs_and_nests

Egg data combined with data on nests

expand_BBS_routes

Expand BBS data to include zeros when a species was not seen.

milk

Mammal milk dataset

NA_to_zero

Change all NA values (missing vlaues) in a column to zero

pikas

Data on presence of pikas and marmots from Front Range Pika Project

plotTukeysHSD

Plot output of TukeyHSD() function when there are 3 groups

sample_BBS_routes

Select random subset of Breeding Bird Survey (BBS) routes

sample_dove_routes

Select random subset of Breeding Bird Survey (BBS) routes

trillium

Data on the size of Trillium from several sites in Crawford County, PA

wetlands

Data on species richness in constructed wetlands at Pennsylvania Game Lands 297 in south western PA.

woodcock_MI_3_years

Subset of Woodcock call survey data from Michigan, USA
